{"tid":1540644,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"Reddit外國網民問題：佢問你答我翻譯！","createTime":"2019-09-04T12:03:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T12:12:46.000Z","uid":184530,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e3a5e8723777aa0dc1f269b98c51cf15affa1406","tid":1540644,"uid":184530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:03:30.000Z","msg":"上reddit r/HongKong<br />\n<br />\n有好多外國網民都唔知道香港人反對d咩<br />\n小弟雖然係垃圾P牌同埋表達能力唔太強，但係希望出一份力<br />\n<br />\n我會定期係連登開英文有關reddit上既問題，尋求高人解答，再自行翻譯放上Reddit.<br />\n<br />\n但我希望大家可以幫我集思廣益，等我可以集中於翻譯上嘅工作<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KZeJef1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKZeJef1.png&h=c0b11f07&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a4d87770b8258af83f5572cc6f218573b9fef59","tid":1540644,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:04:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e82e843fd163825b2d0a15d595683a5a6f73a815","tid":1540644,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:05:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[緊急] <br />\n有 Twitter Account ,  Reddit 既 <br />\n<br />\n陣間 20:45 開始 要不斷將 民記既直播 LINK <br />\n散出去<br />\n貼出去<br />\nTwitter <br />\n<br />\n民記一定會幫我地解釋 0904 並不是勝利日 </span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"5ddea1b4a02eca8909d52f138bf2aefc841b373c","tid":1540644,"uid":288648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:05:27.000Z","msg":"要贏國際輿論就同我入嚟， 人哋根本唔知你哋啲口號up乜鳩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1540527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1540527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1fd62459deff572cf5d6f999bfb85941f35c6ea3","tid":1540644,"uid":184530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:05:31.000Z","msg":"問題1: 佢要講d咩「字眼」先可以令到撤回呢一樣野係清楚地話比全部人聽，而唔會有含糊既地方"},{"pid":"dbfc1c9f2872f994eafc228da3ec617d8089d48c","tid":1540644,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:05:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f729f258abd9ec04858475c5258aa6962bf6805","tid":1540644,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fd62459deff572cf5d6f999bfb85941f35c6ea3","tid":1540644,"uid":184530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:05:31.000Z","msg":"問題1: 佢要講d咩「字眼」先可以令到撤回呢一樣野係清楚地話比全部人聽，而唔會有含糊既地方"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:05:46.000Z","msg":"五大訴求"},{"pid":"365c562fad8ad6b12283305528361860d0c6f464","tid":1540644,"uid":233009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:05:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ca338744b3273619148602298687ffe0de93329f","tid":1540644,"uid":287594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:06:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QUGSMa3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQUGSMa3.gif&h=1c74332a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【長期抗爭】最簡單有效嘅日常抗爭<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538155\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538155</a>"},{"pid":"e0e6d7391d9461bdc67773a196c5fd7044eb0fb9","tid":1540644,"uid":268725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:06:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https: